text: Maria de la Soledad Teresa O'Brien (born September 19, 1966) is an American broadcast journalist. She does broadcasts for CNN and HBO. She has received an Emmy Award. O'Brien was born in St. James, New York. ==References== Category:Television personalities from New York (state) Category:Journalists from New York (state) Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Emmy Award winners
